{"tid":915478,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"比特幣跌穿 4000 美元 重挫後現 420 天新低","createTime":"2018-11-25T04:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T04:41:28.000Z","uid":63184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7ec66f3a51c040bef64730b373cdc23dc936046b","tid":915478,"uid":63184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T04:30:07.000Z","msg":"比特幣跌穿 4000 美元 重挫後現 420 天新低<br />\n安菲\t  /   2018-11-25<br />\n<br />\n比特幣價格自 11 月中旬起，出現明顯波動。在比特幣現金（BCH）硬分叉後，比特幣連番下挫，截至周日 25 日中午（UTC+8）價格落在 3723 美元，相較在比特幣現金硬分叉前（11 月 14 日）每顆比特幣報約 6400 美元下跌超過四成。<br />\n<br />\n同時，比特幣價格僅在過去七天已下跌超過 1,800 美元。在去年瘋狂的牛市，比特幣一度在去年 12 月創下歷史最高價約為 20,000 美元，然而，一年還沒過去，現已跌逾八成，跌穿 4000 美元後更現 420 天新低。<br />\n<br />\n比特幣下挫牽動整個加密貨幣市場呈一片鮮紅，11 月 18 日整體市值在 1850 億美元，截稿時已蒸發逾 650 億美元，整體市值在 1200 億美元以下，這是自 2017 年 9 月以來的低點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://blockcast.it/2018/11/25/below-4k-bitcoins-price-drops-to-a-420-day-low/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblockcast.it%2F2018%2F11%2F25%2Fbelow-4k-bitcoins-price-drops-to-a-420-day-low%2F&d=HyPHtKP0X271k9gPNCCtZ4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=9615e361\" target=\"_blank\">https://blockcast.it/2018/11/25/below-4k-bitcoins-price-drops-to-a-420-day-low/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6f6577affa74082009bb6c750f10ef2f40474f0","tid":915478,"uid":152790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T04:35:28.000Z","msg":"跌到咁上下大部分礦場收入追唔到營運成本<br />\n越黎越少人掘<br />\n最終就會有人可以一方面提供到50%算力<br />\nBtc正式玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673e780ef8f7348842cf87144e6e194df0a376d7","tid":915478,"uid":147097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T04:39:12.000Z","msg":"drop to zero<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a8581368f0175f9676a5a